			<div class="smallfont">A Divider, Not a Uniter</div>
			<div class="smallfont"><img src="images/supporter.gif" alt="" border="" /><br /><img src="images/supporter.gif" alt="" border="" /></div>
			

			
				<div class="smallfont">
					&nbsp;<br /><a href="member.php?u=91"><img src="image.php?u=91&amp;dateline=1197559849" width="54" height="54" alt="Torcer Arcana's Avatar" border="0" /></a>
